{"type":null,"faqId":43473,"title":"为什么设置了图案解锁，亮屏后不显示？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">需要滑动一下屏幕，会出现图案解锁框</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>操作方式：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>EMUI3.1：“设置 </span><span class=\"s1\">&gt; </span><span>全部设置 </span><span class=\"s1\">&gt; </span><span>隐私和安全 </span><span class=\"s1\">&gt; </span><span>锁屏和密码 </span><span class=\"s1\">&gt; </span><span>仅使用密码解锁“，开启即可。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>EMUI3.0及以下版本：“设置 </span><span class=\"s1\">&gt; </span><span>全部设置 </span><span class=\"s1\">&gt; </span><span>隐私和安全 </span><span class=\"s1\">&gt; </span><span>安全 </span><span class=\"s1\">&gt; </span><span>直接显示密码锁屏界面“，开启即可</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8974","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442399014000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10","visitedTimes":3,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"图案,解锁","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}